sequenceDiagram
    participant C as 调用方
    participant M as loadAndCacheMarketplace
    participant G as cacheMarketplaceFromGit
    participant H as cacheMarketplaceFromUrl
    participant F as 文件系统

    C->>M: source={source:'github', repo:'anthropics/...'}
    M->>G: SSH → 失败 → HTTPS 降级
    G-->>M: 克隆到缓存目录
    M-->>C: LoadedPluginMarketplace

    C->>M: source={source:'url', url:'https://...'}
    M->>H: axios.get(url, headers)
    H-->>M: 写入 .json 缓存
    M-->>C: LoadedPluginMarketplace

    C->>M: source={source:'directory', path:'/local/...'}
    M->>F: resolve(path) + 直接读取
    F-->>M: marketplace.json
    M-->>C: LoadedPluginMarketplace
